{
  "text": "This section will focus on designing a U total to achieve the cylinder trajectory tracking. Firstly, we will develop a desired compensation control law (DCCL) [CITATION_1] for cylinder trajectory tracking from the mechanical side in sec 3.1. Secondly, an h(\u00b7) function will be proposed to support the design of a pressure (hydraulic force) tracking error based compressible energy storage function in sec 3.2 to account for the pressure tracking error. Finally, both effects are considered together to develop U total in sec 3.3.",
